swiftdeploy — declarative deployment CLI
Usage:
  swiftdeploy init
  swiftdeploy validate
  swiftdeploy deploy
  swiftdeploy promote [canary|stable]
  swiftdeploy teardown [--clean]
  swiftdeploy status
  swiftdeploy audit
"""

